Package: gl-tailscale-fix
Version: {{VERSION}}
Architecture: all
Maintainer: RemoteToHome Consulting <https://remotetohome.io>
Section: net
Priority: optional
Description: Tailscale enhancements for GL.iNet routers
 Adds features that complement GL's native Tailscale integration:
 a kernel-level policy-routing kill switch (IPv4 and IPv6) that
 survives tailscaled crashes, guest network routing through the
 Tailscale exit node, optional Tailscale SSH toggle for ACL-based
 authentication, and a Tailscale binary version manager. On
 firmware 4.9+, the plugin auto-adapts to coexist with GL's native
 Tailscale features.
 https://remotetohome.io/gl-tailscale-fix
